                | Feel free to contact me...
              // Form
              .form-group-modern.maxw-400x
                form(action='#' method='get')
                  fieldset
                    p.mt-1x
                      label  Name
                      input#firstName(placeholder='First Name' type='text' required='')
                    p.mt-1x
                      label E-mail
                      input#email(placeholder='Email' type='email' required='')
                    p.mt-1x
                      label(for='message') What's your story?
                      textarea#message(name='message' rows='5' cols='33') Message
                    p.font-size-12.font-color-dark-3x.mt-1x
                      | If you're a coach or network marketer who wants to make or
                      | attract with ease, the is for you.
                    p
